              "measure": "CINV severity",
              "description": "The Symptom Management Checklist will measure the presence and severity of nausea and vomiting. Participants will be sent a text link every day for 6 days after chemotherapy or complete this data on a form at home. This starts right after time 1. Nausea will be reported on a 0-10 scale. Higher numbers equal more nausea.",
              "timeFrame": "From baseline1 through the end of the study at 12 or 24 weeks"
            }
